01:13:56,098 --> 01:13:58,266
Apa sebenarnya arti "cinta" itu?

929
01:13:58,266 --> 01:14:01,144
Ada yang tahu?

930
01:14:01,144 --> 01:14:02,646
Tom.

931
01:14:02,646 --> 01:14:05,732
