Hei, Tom.

974
01:22:04,169 --> 01:22:06,671
Kurasa aku akan temui kau disini.

975
01:22:13,387 --> 01:22:16,723
Aku suka tempat ini
sejak kau bawa aku kemari.

976
01:22:16,723 --> 01:22:19,475
Jadi aku...

977
01:22:19,475 --> 01:22:21,894
Aku harus ucapkan selamat.

978
01:22:23,522 --> 01:22:25,481
Hanya jika kau sungguh-sungguh.

979
01:22:25,481 --> 01:22:28,359
Dalam hal itu...

980
01:22:35,200 --> 01:22:37,994
Kau baik saja?

981
01:22:37,994 --> 01:22:38,714
Sehat.

982
01:22:46,879 --> 01:22:49,005
Aku suka setelanmu./Terima kasih.

983
01:22:49,005 --> 01:22:51,382
Kau kelihatan gagah.

984
01:22:51,382 --> 01:22:54,552
