1055
01:28:51,325 --> 01:28:54,286
Ya./Aku tak pernah melihatmu.

1056
01:28:56,039 --> 01:28:58,666
Kau pasti tak memperhatikan sekitar.

1057
01:28:58,666 --> 01:29:00,751
Jika Tom telah mempelajari sesuatu,

1058
01:29:00,751 --> 01:29:03,879
