1074
01:29:51,094 --> 01:29:53,721
kau mau minum kopi bersamaku?

1075
01:29:53,721 --> 01:29:55,806
Oh, maaf.

1076
01:29:55,806 --> 01:29:59,935
Aku harus ketemu seseorang
setelah ini.

